description:
In this "Path To Great Sound" saxophone lesson series from Pro Music Tutor, world-famous saxophonist Andy Sheppard provides you with the basic saxophone techniques that will help you to develop your playing ability now and in the future.

To view this lesson please click here http://www.promusictutor.com/sax/sax-techniques/path-to-a-great-sound-andy-sheppard-sax-lesson
